name: IOUserAudioObject
desc: The base class for most classes in the framework.

items.name: - init
items.desc: Initializes an instance of the audio object base class.

items.name: - GetClassID
items.desc: Gets the audio class identifier of the object.

items.name: - GetBaseClassID
items.desc: Gets the audio class identifier of the base class object.

items.name: - GetWorkQueue
items.desc: Gets the work queue created by the audio object, as a pointer to a dispatch queue.

items.name: - GetName
items.desc: Gets the name of the object.

items.name: - SetName
items.desc: Sets the name of the object.

items.name: - AddCustomProperty
items.desc: Adds a custom property to the audio object.

items.name: - RemoveCustomProperty
items.desc: Removes a previously-added custom property object from the audio object.
